raw_text = "~ start
Nina: How do you know that Naomi bitch?
PlayerM: Hi Nina! 😅 She's my friend
PlayerM: She's really nice actually, maybe you two could talk?
Nina: Nah, whatever
Nina: Look I'm not here to talk about miss take-pictures-for-fun club
Nina: I wanna talk about YOU
PlayerM: Me? 😳
Nina: You've been in college for a while now
Nina: And what have you done with it?
Nina: Sat in class, texted your boyfriend, went to bed early?
PlayerM: I mean... yeah? 😅
Nina: That's exactly my point
Nina: I've seen so many girls completely waste their college years
Nina: Then they graduate and realize they didn't actually LIVE
Nina: And they regret it for the rest of their sad and boring lives
PlayerM: That sounds scary actually 😟
Nina: It IS scary
Nina: You're in your prime right now Maple
PlayerM: Mabel*
Nina: You have to push yourself to be on top
Nina: Your boyfriend just wants you all to himself 
Nina: He's not seeing what's best for you
Nina: Does he really do anything for you? Visit you? Treat you perfectly?
PlayerM: Nobody is perfect Nina 😅 Mom taught me that
Nina: But you can still have a perfect college experience you'll never regret
Nina: That's all that matters
PlayerM: Oh... I kind of get what you're saying
Nina: Embrace yourself Maple and find out who you really are babe
PlayerM: Mabel*
Nina: Most people don't until it's too late
Nina: I just don't want that for you
Nina: You've got something about you, I can tell
PlayerM: You really think so? 🥺
Nina: I know so
Nina: So listen to me, I'm experienced and older
Nina: Think of me as your big sis who's always right Maple
PlayerM: Mabel*
PlayerM: Sure, I'll try to trust you more often 😣
PlayerM: So I should join the sorority?
Nina: HELL YEAH
Nina: You join us and make memories you won't ever forget 😉
Nina: Did I spell all that right?
PlayerM: You did 😳
Nina: There IS one requirement to join the sorority though
PlayerM: What is it?
Nina: You gotta send a pic of your tits 😘
PlayerM: WHAT?? 😱
Nina: It's standard, every girl does it when they apply
Nina: I had to do it too
Nina: img: nina/18
Nina: See? No big deal
PlayerM: Oh my god Nina 😳
PlayerM: I don't know if I can do that 🙈
Nina: Come on it's just between us girls
PlayerM: ...
PlayerM: Okay
PlayerM: I mean it's a club requirement right?
PlayerM: And a lot of girls apply right?
PlayerM: And it's just between us girls right?
Nina: Hurry up already 🙄
PlayerM: Give me a second, I've never done this before 🥺
PlayerM: But uhm, I'm gonna cover a little... I'm just too shy 🙈
PlayerM: img: mabel/106
PlayerM: There!! Does that work?? 😣
Nina: LMAOOO
Nina: You actually did it
Nina: I was kidding that's not actually a requirement 😂
PlayerM: NINA!!! 😭😭
PlayerM: Delete that omg
Nina: Relax girl 🙄
Nina: They're just tits
Nina: They're meant to pleasure and be pleasured by hot guys 👅
Nina: The sooner you figure that out the better off you'll be 😘
PlayerM: I can't believe you just did that to me 🥺😭😭
Nina: Remember what I said about big sis stuff?
PlayerM: That's not fair!
Nina: It totally is, see how easy it was to send? 
Nina: That's part of your growth, for your own good babe
PlayerM: 😩
Nina: You'll thank me later pink girl 💋
=> END
